Title: Object: St Mary of Egypt
Description: St Maria of Egypt, praying with her right breast exposed and her hands crossed in front of her body; after Domenichino (?). c.1700 colour mezzotint, printed from four plates.
Producer name: Print made by: Jakob Christoph Le Blon
Curator's comments: For another impression, see 1866,0623.75. For more information on this print and an illustration, see: Rodari (ed): 'Anatomie de la couleur; I'invention de l'estampe en couleurs', cat 48
